snippet.title: Day of the Shell - Official Reveal Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Watch the Day of the Shell reveal trailer for a look at the various colorful environments and gameplay from this upcoming tactical roguelite game. In Day of the Shell, play as a monster hunter, traveling from island to island to defeat the god of the seas. Day of the Shell is coming to PC.
